    <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/7/16/19967354/science-fiction-fantasy-recommendations-books-july-2019-game-of-thrones-george-rr-martin">15 new science fiction and fantasy books to check out in late July </a></h2>
    
    
    
      
        <div class="c-byline" data-cid="site/byline-1587442910_2459_83662" data-cdata='{"timestamp":1563296213}'>
